:: code.labPowerUp [static-storage] {"position":"1600,3775","size":"100,100"}
{=(dialog: [(either: "The room yawns like a great beast awakening to the smell of magic.", "The vehzin begins to glow in the receptacle, and its light flow to all the equipment.", "Machineries - which you can barely comprehend despite years of study - groan and jitter into place.", "The genius of generations of magi stirs to life in these machines. Each cog - now common in all magical laboratories - was a Sacred Opal once.") <br> $cssDesc[Fuel topped up, and workstation is now active. Starting a synthesis job will consume the fuel.]], "✓")